Port the stranded DP24 ring-switching algebra layer from the pre-merge
Binius/RingSwitching Prelude into the new Profile-abstract RingSwitching
Prelude, re-stated over RingSwitchingProfile (φ₀/φ₁/basis/decomposeRows
laws) so it serves every instantiation. New verified lemmas:
embedded_MLP_eval_eq_sum, decomposeRows_sum, packMLE_repr_eval,
decompose_rows_packMLE, eqTilde_prod/concat_split, aeval_eq_sum_eqTilde,
hypercubeSplitEquiv, check_rows_sum_eq_aeval, and the capstone
performCheckOriginalEvaluation_packMLE_iff.

