(was P.decomposeColumns); the column form does not reconstruct t(r) — the
honest tensor's rows carry the φ₁/t' factor. Mirrors the pre-merge
soundness fix. Verifier uses it only as a Bool, so unaffected.

Close BatchingPhase batchingKnowledgeStateFunction.toFun_next round-0
sorry (was L424) via the capstone.

lake env lean: Prelude + BatchingPhase both 0 errors. No new
sorry/axiom/native_decide.

